Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:37.74,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I couldn't understand the feeling of being in touch with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:48.86,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I couldn't understand the feeling of being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:01.21,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihiro, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:02.15,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:09.62,MainF,Kei & Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,L-e-t's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.25,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:20.07,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.43,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.06,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.56,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That small encounter totally changed the path I was walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.82,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that the happy times would continue forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.78,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.27,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Something is on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:36.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I broke our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it seems that way, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.35,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I don't really remember what happened back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:49.96,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Pya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is your cold better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:17.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad that you've recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.69,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.41,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to write a novel with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"Why...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.55,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound fun? Let's try to write one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:57.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You know that my memory doesn't last more than thirteen hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll help you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.73,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to write one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say something so mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Mean? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:12.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You're usually a much kinder person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:17.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try writing a novel for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.10,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:25.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said it was your dream to write stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That was the me from a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.93,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You are you, whether from a week ago or now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A dream is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:49.99,MainT,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I don't understand you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.56,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.73,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't understand myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:03.30,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You broke your promise to me because you met Miyamura-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.88,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kei-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.02,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trade this month's manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.85,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. I haven't bought mine yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.02,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:28.16,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge of getting the monthly magazine, MIMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:32.58,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You can go ahead and read it first, so you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.60,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of money already for the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.00,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I lent some to Hiro-senpai the other day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:38.45,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.05,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Onii-chan borrow money from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:44.20,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hiro-senpai was dumped by Miyamura-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.37,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:50.11,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai was penniless, so I paid the bill for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.01,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're talking about at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.56,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Miyamura-senpai was supposed to treat Hiro-senpai the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:01.21,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai made her mad, and she went home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.35,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Then Onii-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:08.53,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai is as clumsy in relationships with girls as he seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.13,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.38,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It flies pretty well, because it's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I get paid soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, erm... Miyako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't add "san" either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.18,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I won't answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:40.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:44.99,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your obedience, I guess I'll make an exception and forgive you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:48.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive? Did I do something that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's some extraordinary food prepared for our reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:58.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My credit is always in an extraordinary state at the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:00.44,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Poor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.00,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.12,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll treat you for real, so let's go and eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just go strolling around every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.65,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:16.90,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.50,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.13,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Your place of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:33.32,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he doesn't have anything good to eat, since it's the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.07,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.03,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, that girl is Hirono's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.13,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,So it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.18,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, you live in quite a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be a little more cautious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:07.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't just go to a guy's room like it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:09.84,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:10.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.77,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That you'll be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your thinking is too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.65,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That response doesn't sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:26.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,With someone you don't know well, there's no way you could know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:30.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I know what kind of person he is and what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.92,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bragging, but I have a good eye for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.68,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I found an ecchi book!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:46.13,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, so that's what you're into.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.82,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is drawing material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like that sounds plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do my work soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:58.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, go ahead. Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.05,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll observe quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I can't let others see my drafts before they're published.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.41,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me some that have already been published.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.24,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me the manga that you drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'll go home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to make a deal with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,S-h-o-w me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:19.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is a short story I wrote before my works were serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been published as a book yet, so I only have copies of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm borrowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.86,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.09,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, President. I'm taking my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:37.86,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.17,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you're short of equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.94,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I think I'll probably ask you before the next production.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.04,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The Cinema Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:50.54,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The guys were bragging about it, so they'll definitely win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.17,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Are you going to make one by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.21,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There's a film I want to make no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.47,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Mizuki? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.82,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite an arrogant question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.86,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about deliciousness. It's about whether eating it will be harmful or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:25.83,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:30.37,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,How on Earth can you make such bad food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.27,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to put it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:38.27,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's just one, you shouldn't waste rice like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.48,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's not one. It's three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:41.13,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.57,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I made three. This is the rice ball that got finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:48.14,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.89,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,They stuck to my hands while I was molding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.48,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't cook, ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.86,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.59,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:08.04,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'm responsible for it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.04,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.95,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:18.16,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's also partly my fault that Onii-chan is working so hard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.28,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs52}A
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.28,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,This is a parody of an erotic literature's title of the same pronounciation (花と蛇), written by Dan Oniroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:30.16,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs52}A
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.45,0:12:30.16,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,This is another parody of a martial art manga of the same pronounciation (マスカレード) drawn by Itagaki Masaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:26.96,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, look! This one is interesting too. Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:30.14,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Ah, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.73,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.02,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. It looks exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.63,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, draw more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.15,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.33,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You might be a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.69,MainF,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I... wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:49.41,MainF,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.83,MainT,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I was happy to be with Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:00.20,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I was happy to see them happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.92,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.60,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What am I seeking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:14.31,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for the color that's missing from the world I see. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:20.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,When did you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Hirono-kun. Manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm drawing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Not that one. The others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.07,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any other manga that you drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:41.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I still have three more short stories, and the ones that were serialized already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.66,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me those. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:48.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now"...? Is my manga that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.47,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you're being nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they were {\i1}really{\i0}{\fsp4} {\fsp0.5}interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.54,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You might be a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.53,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:26.34,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mizuki. The pork cutlet is still raw inside, even though the outside is burned black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.18,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the pan's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.39,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean to me. Teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:39.00,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Senpai. For fried food, the temperature of the oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.65,Main2,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.48,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The pan is burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.43,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:50.68,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, don't use water! Absolutely not! The fire will only get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.08,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.97,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayonnaise. Please put mayonnaise on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.99,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Pour a whole ton of it into the pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.90,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,A whole ton of it...? H-Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.67,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:08.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is out, Mizuki! You're an amazing genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.68,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an amazing genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "welcome back."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:32.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better if you stopped hiding the duplicate key under the flowerpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:40.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of making you dinner to thank you for the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:41.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that humans can't digest raw starch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:48.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.84,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that an excessive intake of chemical seasonings makes your hands and feet go numb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.63,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What's that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:59.46,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I wouldn't eat a girl's home cooking as long as I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.99,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you have some kind of dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The only food that my heart allows are these!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:15.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Miyako's specially-made rice with wild herbs is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,So? Are you going to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.17,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:28.84,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:35.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. She's the only one I didn't want to flatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's some compensation if you say it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth making if I'm eating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Alone...? What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,The way you hold your chopsticks is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:53.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're Japanese, you have to hold chopsticks properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have tendonitis. In my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's something like an occupational hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a light case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who only draw when the pain abates, but I'm not that badly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.79,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:20.22,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It is terrible. Not sleeping, not eating. Can't have fun, and can't go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.06,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,"What do I think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:30.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like an idiot who's forcing himself to do the impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Just doing your best makes it worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.70,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun's not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.38,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold the chopsticks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I can eat by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:59.49,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do your work, you have to let your hand rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.94,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:09.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:19.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.97,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs36}A
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.97,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Yume," which means "Dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chihiro. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Give the novel a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say it's your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say there are stories you want to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're saying something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're saying something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a person who's come to a dead end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:56.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,since there's nothing I want to or can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,that's why it's okay if my dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Such a simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:10.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:16.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's right. I'm the one who's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.32,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:51.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why does someone else know me better than I know myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I want to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:05.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only dream left before my memory disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.67,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I really don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:08.76,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:16.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If even that doesn't work out, then I really will have nothing left, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.15,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.62,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.37,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kissing is something lovers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we become lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:37.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean today, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:38.95,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, I would've been glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:46.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I felt really lonely sleeping by myself last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:50.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you, and... I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.48,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The me from yesterday wrote that in my diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:58.24,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:03.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I dislike today's you. But I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please hug me for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:10.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story do you want to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:17.82,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm thinking about writing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:28.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,a story about a girl who's the only survivor in a world where everything's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:03.44,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:07.04,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:08.16,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:10.40,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:11.93,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:13.87,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:19.49,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, this is no good, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:20.87,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't put something on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:23.88,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,the bread becomes soggy after absorbing water from the vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:28.37,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:30.93,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:38.81,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,The woven story is a lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:43.79,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ef - a tale of memories:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.22,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.70,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
